      <title>Re: Complete title suggestion</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ngsuggest/forum/general/complete_title_suggestion/re_complete_title_suggestion</link>
      <description>Possible.&#13;
&#13;
The main "catch" is that solr is tokenizing the words of all text so to avoid this you should suggest terms form a solr field which is "string" solr type. That string solr type is not tokenized but rather used as a single token&#13;
&#13;
Hope this helps</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Ivo Lukač)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/ngsuggest/forum/general/complete_title_suggestion/re_complete_title_suggestion</guid>
