      <title>Re: installation issues</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ngsuggest/forum/general/installation_issues/re_installation_issues5</link>
      <description>Usually custom extensions need to be ordered before default ones. Problem is that you can't sort it from the admini interface (yet), you need to edit your site.ini override by hand.&#13;
&#13;
So put the order like this:&#13;
ActiveExtensions[]=ngsuggest&#13;
ActiveExtensions[]=ezfind&#13;
ActiveExtensions[]=ezflow&#13;
ActiveExtensions[]=ezwebin&#13;
</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Ivo Lukač)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/ngsuggest/forum/general/installation_issues/re_installation_issues5</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Aug 2010 14:33:52 +0000</pubDate>
